HEADWORD: Thecla
<hw>Thec"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any one of many
species of small delicately colored butterflies belonging to
<gen>Thecla</gen> and allied genera; -- called also
<altname>hairstreak</altname>, and <altname>elfin</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

